Description
org.interworldtransport.cladosG
Provides the geometry classes and the structures needed for multi-algebra geometric models.

    Blade
    A (@code Blade) is essentially an outer product space built from 0 to many vectors.If the vectors aren't parallel, the blade is of higher rank than a vector.
